<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mamaearth – Country Redirect</title>
  <!-- Favicon from mamaearth.com -->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="https://mamaearth.com/cdn/shop/files/cropped-Favicon-2-150x150.png">
  <style>
    :root {
      --green: #1fad7e;
      --blue: #00afef;
      --pink: #ff5b6f;
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--blue));
      color: #333;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: #222;
    }
    p {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #0f9065;
    }
    .warning {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #777;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .card {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://mamaearth.com/cdn/shop/files/mama.svg" alt="Mamaearth logo">
    </div>
    <h1>You’re on our India site</h1>
    <p>The domain <strong>mamaearth.in</strong> caters exclusively to customers in India. <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--green);">To place an order from your country, please visit us at mamaearth.com.</span></p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn" href="https://mamaearth.com">Visit mamaearth.com</a>
    </div>
    <p class="warning">Warning:&nbsp;The domain, logo and other properties belongs to Honasa Consumer Ltd, using them without consent is a violation.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>